name: SÌ EAU DE PARFUM EDITION LIMITÉE 2020
description: In 2020, to celebrate Christmas, Giorgio Armani is thinking big and is offering a limited and colourful edition of his iconic product: SÌ Eau de Parfum. Sì is a tribute to modern femininity, an irresistible blend of grace, strength and a spirit of independence. This fragrance is a modern chypre, which is chic and voluptuous.
